read a .csv file (to keep it very simple) into an array (or arraylist to be able to continually make it bigger).

four functions:

(1) add
  Be able to add a new todo task. Each task includes title, due date, id, and notes.
(2) delete
  Delete a task based on id
(3) edit
  Choose a task based on id, and edit it
(4) list
  A little more feature rich command, should be able to do
  simple sorting and searching (fuzzy).

File structure:
id,title,done,due date,note